OL,5, A council is facing equal pay claims   
OL,6, from thousands of women, according to a
OL,7, union which alleges some workers are   
OL,8, missing out on up to #11,000.          
OL,10,FSheffield City Council is the latest   
OL,11,Fauthority to face action after the GMB 
OL,12,Funion launched a claim on Monday.      
OL,14,FUnion organisers say they want the     
OL,15,Fcouncil to commit to a full review of  
OL,16,Fall equal pay issues identified.       
OL,18,FThe council's deputy leader said staff 
OL,19,Fwere encouraged to raise concerns about
OL,20,Fequal pay with the authority directly. 
